name: Alyona X
description: My name is Alyona. I am 25 years old. I love nature very much. That is why I try to find free time to go outside the city. Moreover i adore playing the piano and singing. I love reading interesting books – my favorite kinds of books are fantasy and romantic novels. I adore playing the piano and singing. I go to the gym almost every day, it is good chance to keep my body in good shape. I want to share my life with kind, manly, smart man, with good sense of humor. I appreciate respect, understanding, loyalty between each others . I am ready to surround my beloved with care and love. I need my special one who will be the part of my heart which is missing at the moment.
